{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 13 shows the effect of the digital twin on the fault diagnosis results.",
    "The results improve when the digital twin model is used for fault diagnosis.",
    "The diagnostic accuracy without the digital twin model is generally below 90%.",
    "The accuracy of the digital twin model can be more than 90%.",
    "The experimental results demonstrate that digital twin systems improve the accuracy of fault diagnosis."
  ]
}